Class MimeMessageImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.mail.Message
      • javax.mail.internet.MimeMessage
        • com.sun.mail.smtp.SMTPMessage

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MimePart, Part
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReadMostlyMimeMessage

    public class MimeMessageImpl
extends SMTPMessage
    Extends MimeMessage by overriding the MimeMessage.updateHeaders() method to not modify the "Message-ID". Also provides implementations for Message.getReceivedDate() and SMTPMessage.getEnvelopeFrom() by subclassing SMTPMessage.
